			<change xml:lang="EN">
				<p sameAs="title"></p>
				<p sameAs="summary"></p>
				<p sameAs="settingDesc">These two letters were used as evidence in a lawsuit related to unpaid rents, moved by Manuel Caetano Pacheco de Melo against António Geraldes de Teive e Sampaio in 1779. The letters are from 1769, ten years before the lawsuit was moved. The answer to the first letter (PSCR1538) was given in the lower left corner, partially covered by the fold of the file and in faint handwriting.</p>
				<p sameAs="text"></p></change>
		</revisionDesc>
